Tables
======
Some Markdown processors (like MD4C `md2html`) support GitHub-style tables:

| Column 1       | Column 2       |
| -------------- | -------------- |
| row 1 column 1 | row 1 column 2 |
| row 2 column 1 | row 2 column 2 |
| row 3 column 1 | row 3 column 2 |
| row 4 column 1 | row 4 column 2 |

